commit message: We should not need to synchronize here

Simplify how the hosts list is handled (switch to ArrayAdapter) and reduce resource usage by not creating a new SimpleAdapter every time. Also reduce load by only sending a map from the threads doing work instead of sending a list of maps each time to a new adapter
Clear the list each time a host discovery is performed

Override equals method on the hashmap that holds host entries, if an entry already exists we can assume that we need to update it with the netbios result, use more threads when processing the found hosts
Use GravityCompat.START to better handle right-to-left cases
